          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/goodull/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1834410-4.jpg" alt="蒿艾离离" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36695108/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36695108/" class="">第141页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/goodull/" class=" " title="蒿艾离离">蒿艾离离</a>
                (不要相信晴空，海啸一定会来)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36695108">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">所谓“名教”，即“以名为教”，它依据名分关系制定出一整套道德规范。名分关系最主要的有三项:即君臣关系、父子关系、夫妇关系，儒家称之为“三纲”。社会种种关系好比是一张大网，网要靠纲绳来控制，儒家认为，抓住了君臣、父子、夫妇这三纲，就可以控制整个社会。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-12-04 00:23</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
